Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第五只了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚做的不错啊  茜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家做到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有六支
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天召集大家来是为了另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上是关于下次的实力测验的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡眠不足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚毕竟弄到很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  水羽老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不觉得没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午的时候你打瞌睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近也经常忘记作业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小测验的结果也是很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我觉得这是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜每天都要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Alone像昨天一样出现得太晚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有学习的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的事情和这件事也有关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上各科教师都向我狠狠告过状了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果下次的实力测验你还是不及格的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要禁止你当前的打工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且直到下一次测验都要每天来学校接受补习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现这种情况的话  也会妨碍到Vivid队伍的活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的情况下  可能要动用军队的情报部门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你的成绩进行操作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以耍诈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个  水羽老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也想做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去小茜家学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们教你学习应付测验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能来帮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我大概就能安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真是一只好队伍啊  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  星期六见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空闲的时间也只有星期六一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天回去也要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是没有时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小茜小学的时候成绩很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真教她的话一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事  我可以再请一个人来我们的学习会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  吓到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这星期六你有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实力测验也临近了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们打算星期六去小茜家开学习会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  我想请你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那天我有很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  吓到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  黑骑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能陪我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上小茜她们要开学习会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话  黑骑同学要不要一起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那一天我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  好遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果你有时间了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以和我们说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  打扰下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六  有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上  小茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙的  要学习的话你们自己学好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然很怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  比司吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们干嘛这么照顾我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我绝对无法允许
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去干涉别人  但每天都去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是我们最初的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作Alone破坏掉示现引擎  这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还特意要去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他们的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无需持有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果与破坏示现引擎相关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种程度上可以允许你胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  除此之外一定要遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是只能尽快破坏掉示现引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不能只依靠Alone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能知道它的更多弱点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示现引擎设计者  一色健次郎博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的孙女…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一色茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临  久候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们三个人一起来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  小零
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  一色博士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说可能又要在Blue Island上过夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是来玩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围裙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  我们各自准备了各科要点的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这个就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个不懂事的姐姐  就拜托大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点不像姐姐  完美的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  小零
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  小零比较擅长哪一科啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像都很擅长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的成绩和若叶一样好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵擅长的科目和不擅长的科目区分太明显了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么语文一科连平均分都拿不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  文学很浪漫的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  黑骑同学是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比起书本  更喜欢花草和动物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  你和燕鸥的关系也很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在喂它们什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借厕所用一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  从那里出去后左转到尽头就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在干什么啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从外部观测来看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色博士的研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在右手边的独栋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  这样的话X就会被消去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色健次郎制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是一色博士的发明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天元理心流  丧心击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在厨房跌倒后失去知觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确  正确  正确  20题正确19题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  你只要做的话就能做得到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因学习疲劳的身体正渴求能量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么差不多也该吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚去买东西了  大家也一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  能到园子里去摘些蔬菜来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合防卫军总司令部紧急来电
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厉害啊  都是小茜照料的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和小桃一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄瓜上长着刺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个奇怪的人  一色同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种充满干劲的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜她会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对想要成为朋友的人  就会充满干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我也没有理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和若叶  向日葵相遇之后就感觉有点懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种充满干劲的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样互相吸引  于是我们就在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小茜是我们的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有股太阳的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们三个  脸上都沾着蛋黄酱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我舔  我舔  我舔  我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小零也吃一个吧  肯定好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好朋友番茄  真幸运呢  一定会有好事情发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事情…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  比如愿望成真什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小零  不可以糟蹋食物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起点事  先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小零
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小零
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛和他们一起欢笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个我才到这个世界来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到你出场了  零
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是电磁波攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用电缆或天线发出强波形电流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让接触到的电子产品的器件和回路受损的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说就是用强电磁波来破坏周围的电器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  这是Alone通过的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那个Alone现在正往Blue Island笔直前进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说这么下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的首都机能将崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会造成多大的损失  不可想象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听好了  一定要在此拦下它  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Texture  On
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃的晚餐还等着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Rang
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Impact
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是感觉不像会停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  要趁现在干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是市区  有残骸坠落就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Vivid Collider一口气解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid Yellow
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎突破临界点  输出200%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我射中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Final Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  放松下来之后肚子就饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  思想传到我这来了  小茜满脑子都是吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算在到达海边前阻止下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我制作的Vivid System  理所当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点奇怪  Alone的反应就是不消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还不快点回来呢  大家
